de.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Rpow/Basic.html#CFC.sqrt\">CFC.sqrt</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Rpow/Basic.html#CFC.sqrt\">CFC.sqrt</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>), <span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/SelfAdjoint.html#IsSelfAdjoint\">IsSelfAdjoint</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a>     <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>), <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Notation/Defs.html#Star.star\">star</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>), <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Notation/Defs.html#Star.star\">star</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Notation.html#PosPart.posPart\">⁺</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/SelfAdjoint.html#IsSelfAdjoint\">IsSelfAdjoint</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Notation.html#NegPart.negPart\">⁻</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">,</a>     <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/SelfAdjoint.html#IsSelfAdjoint\">IsSelfAdjoint</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Spectrum/Quasispectrum.html#QuasispectrumRestricts\">QuasispectrumRestricts</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Instances/NNReal/Lemmas.html#ContinuousMap.realToNNReal\">ContinuousMap.realToNNReal</a></span></span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">]</a>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/List/TFAE.html#List.TFAE\">TFAE</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For an element `a` in a C⋆-algebra, TFAE:\n1. `0 ≤ a`\n2. `a = sqrt a * sqrt a`\n3. `a = b * b` for some nonnegative `b`\n4. `a = b * b` for some self-adjoint `b`\n5. `a = star b * b` for some `b`\n6. `a = b * star b` for some `b`\n7. `a = a⁺`\n8. `a` is self-adjoint and `a⁻ = 0`\n9. `a` is self-adjoint and has nonnegative spectrum ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Rpow/Basic.html#CStarAlgebra.nonneg_TFAE","kind":"theorem","line":350,"name":"CStarAlgebra.nonneg_TFAE","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprove